WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.665
Most people who install a coding

00:00:02.665 --> 00:00:05.330
agent harness use it in first

00:00:05.330 --> 00:00:07.995
gear. They connect a model, ask

00:00:07.995 --> 00:00:10.660
a few chat questions, and plateau

00:00:10.660 --> 00:00:13.325
there. The powerful features, skills, context

00:00:13.325 --> 00:00:15.990
files, MCP servers, subagents, are invisible

00:00:15.990 --> 00:00:18.655
and intimidating. Garnish fixes that by

00:00:18.655 --> 00:00:21.320
turning the harness into a game.

00:00:21.320 --> 00:00:23.985
Garnish is a gamified onboarding layer

00:00:23.985 --> 00:00:26.650
for agentic coding harnesses. You start

00:00:26.650 --> 00:00:29.315
with agent chat and nothing else.

00:00:29.315 --> 00:00:31.980
You level up by completing quests

00:00:31.980 --> 00:00:34.645
that are verified against real behavior,

00:00:34.645 --> 00:00:37.311
not self-reported checkboxes. Completing quests unlocks

00:00:37.311 --> 00:00:39.976
the next tier of harness features,

00:00:39.976 --> 00:00:42.641
which physically appear in the harness

00:00:42.641 --> 00:00:45.306
as they unlock. Three properties make

00:00:45.306 --> 00:00:47.971
it work. First, quests run through

00:00:47.971 --> 00:00:50.636
a real harness against real files.

00:00:50.636 --> 00:00:53.301
Second, the agent is the tutor.

00:00:53.301 --> 00:00:55.966
The active quest is injected into

00:00:55.966 --> 00:00:58.631
the harness context, so the agent

00:00:58.631 --> 00:01:01.296
you are learning to use is

00:01:01.296 --> 00:01:03.961
also your guide. Third, feature gating

00:01:03.961 --> 00:01:06.626
keeps the surface area matched to

00:01:06.626 --> 00:01:09.291
your competence. It is built with

00:01:09.291 --> 00:01:11.956
Bun and TypeScript. Two artifacts share

00:01:11.956 --> 00:01:14.621
one core library. A thin CLI

00:01:14.621 --> 00:01:17.286
handles onboarding and status outside a

00:01:17.286 --> 00:01:19.951
session. A Pi extension runs in-process

00:01:19.951 --> 00:01:22.616
inside the harness, observing live events,

00:01:22.616 --> 00:01:25.281
rendering a HUD, and applying unlocks.

00:01:25.281 --> 00:01:27.946
The core library has five modules.

00:01:27.946 --> 00:01:30.611
Domain schemas define quests, levels, and

00:01:30.611 --> 00:01:33.276
checks using Zod with branded types.

00:01:33.276 --> 00:01:35.941
The pack loader validates curriculum files

00:01:35.941 --> 00:01:38.606
and builds the quest graph, rejecting

00:01:38.606 --> 00:01:41.271
cycles and unknown IDs. The verifier

00:01:41.271 --> 00:01:43.936
evaluates checks against live events and

00:01:43.936 --> 00:01:46.601
on-demand probes. The progression engine folds

00:01:46.601 --> 00:01:49.267
an append-only event log into state.

00:01:49.267 --> 00:01:51.932
And the Pi adapter isolates all

00:01:51.932 --> 00:01:54.597
harness-specific knowledge behind one seam. Running

00:01:54.597 --> 00:01:57.262
garnish init installs a certified Pi

00:01:57.262 --> 00:01:59.927
runtime into Garnish-owned storage. It asks

00:01:59.927 --> 00:02:02.592
three onboarding questions, scaffolds a disposable

00:02:02.592 --> 00:02:05.257
sandbox, and launches an isolated session.

00:02:05.257 --> 00:02:07.922
Your global harness config is never

00:02:07.922 --> 00:02:10.587
touched. The extension performs a startup

00:02:10.587 --> 00:02:13.252
version handshake and pauses quests if

00:02:13.252 --> 00:02:15.917
the runtime does not match. When

00:02:15.917 --> 00:02:18.582
you complete a quest, the extension

00:02:18.582 --> 00:02:21.247
observes real harness events. The verifier

00:02:21.247 --> 00:02:23.912
evaluates declarative checks against those events

00:02:23.912 --> 00:02:26.577
and on-demand file, command, and git

00:02:26.577 --> 00:02:29.242
probes. No LLM grading. Everything is

00:02:29.242 --> 00:02:31.907
deterministic. The whole path is designed

00:02:31.907 --> 00:02:34.572
for sub-ten-second feedback. Quests declare checks

00:02:34.572 --> 00:02:37.237
in a closed DSL. Nine check

00:02:37.237 --> 00:02:39.902
types cover harness events, file existence,

00:02:39.902 --> 00:02:42.567
JSON and YAML config paths, command

00:02:42.567 --> 00:02:45.232
exit codes, git state, MCP handshakes,

00:02:45.232 --> 00:02:47.897
skill validity, and user confirmation. The

00:02:47.897 --> 00:02:50.562
set only grows by architectural decision.

00:02:50.562 --> 00:02:53.227
Completing quests unlocks harness features. The

00:02:53.227 --> 00:02:55.892
gate catalog maps each feature to

00:02:55.892 --> 00:02:58.557
Pi config surfaces. Tools apply live

00:02:58.557 --> 00:03:01.223
through setActiveTools. Skills and extensions require

00:03:01.223 --> 00:03:03.888
a session reload. Unlocks are monotonic.

00:03:03.888 --> 00:03:06.553
Capabilities are only ever added, never

00:03:06.553 --> 00:03:09.218
removed. State lives in an append-only

00:03:09.218 --> 00:03:11.883
event log. A pure function folds

00:03:11.883 --> 00:03:14.548
the log into the current state,

00:03:14.548 --> 00:03:17.213
completed quests, XP, badges, and unlocked

00:03:17.213 --> 00:03:19.878
capabilities. Delete the state file and

00:03:19.878 --> 00:03:22.543
replay reconstructs everything. Crash-safe, auditable, replayable.

00:03:22.543 --> 00:03:25.208
The curriculum uses a gamer-native theme.

00:03:25.208 --> 00:03:27.873
Tutorial Island for onboarding. First Quest

00:03:27.873 --> 00:03:30.538
for the core agent loop. Lore

00:03:30.538 --> 00:03:33.203
for context management. Five more levels

00:03:33.203 --> 00:03:35.868
are planned, from Skill Tree through

00:03:35.868 --> 00:03:38.533
Loadout, The Party, and Macros, to

00:03:38.533 --> 00:03:41.198
a Final Boss capstone. The codebase

00:03:41.198 --> 00:03:43.863
is four days old. Five thousand

00:03:43.863 --> 00:03:46.528
four hundred lines of TypeScript source,

00:03:46.528 --> 00:03:49.193
four thousand eight hundred lines of

00:03:49.193 --> 00:03:51.858
tests. That near one-to-one test ratio

00:03:51.858 --> 00:03:54.523
reflects a fixture-driven proof plan. The

00:03:54.523 --> 00:03:57.188
largest file is the verifier at

00:03:57.188 --> 00:03:59.853
nine hundred thirty-six lines, the main

00:03:59.853 --> 00:04:02.518
complexity hotspot. A v2 direction is

00:04:02.518 --> 00:04:05.183
already captured. Garnish will build its

00:04:05.183 --> 00:04:07.848
own purpose-built harness and TUI, dropping

00:04:07.848 --> 00:04:10.514
the Pi dependency. The curriculum and

00:04:10.514 --> 00:04:13.179
engine survive the rewrite. The adapter

00:04:13.179 --> 00:04:15.844
and extension get replaced. Garnish teaches

00:04:15.844 --> 00:04:18.509
agentic coding craft by doing. Real

00:04:18.509 --> 00:04:21.174
harness, real quests, real verification. Earn

00:04:21.174 --> 00:04:22.062
your complexity.
